  <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="AP22_is_equal_in_time_to">
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">AP22 is equal in time to</rdfs:label>
    <skos:notation>AP22</skos:notation>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">is equal in time to</skos:prefLabel>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E2_Temporal_Entity"/>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E2_Temporal_Entity"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P175_starts_before_or_with_the_start_of"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P175i_starts_after_or_with_the_start_of"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P184_ends_before_or_with_the_end_of"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P184i_ends_with_or_after_the_end_of"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Quantification: many to many (0,n:0,n)

Scope note:
This property symmetrically identifies a situation in which the starting point and the ending point for an instance of E2 Temporal Entity is equal to the starting point and the ending point of another instance of E2 Temporal Entity, respectively.
This property is only necessary if the time span is unknown (otherwise the equivalence can be calculated).
This property is the same as the "equal" relationship of Allen’s temporal logic (Allen, 1983, pp. 832-843).
This property is transitive.

Examples:
- The burning of the Temple of Artemis at Ephesus (E6) is equal in time to the birth of Alexander the Great E69 [on July 6, 356 BC as reported by Plutarch in Vitae Parallelae, III, 3]. (Plutarch, 1919)

In First Order Logic:
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ E2(x)
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ E2(y)
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ P175(x,y)
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ P175i(x,y)
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ P184(x,y)
- AP22(x,y) ⇒ P184i(x,y)
</rdfs:comment>
  </owl:ObjectProperty>
  <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="AP23_finishes">
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">AP23 finishes</rdfs:label>
    <skos:notation>AP23</skos:notation>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">finishes</skos:prefLabel>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E2_Temporal_Entity"/>
